INTERNATIONAL ATOMIC ENERGY AGENCY, Safety Series No.3,     
"Advisory Material for the Application of the IAEA Transport
Regulations", Vienna, 1973, STI/PUB/324.
<P>
<A NAME="approve"><HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
