<CENTER><H3>African Regional Co-operative Agreement for Research, Development and Training Related to Nuclear Science and Technology
<P>
<SMALL>Extension of Agreement</SMALL></H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<OL>
<LI>Pursuant to Article XIV.2, the Agreement "shall continue in force for a period of five years from the date of its entry into force and may be extended for further periods of five years if the Government Parties so agree".
<P>
<LI>The extension of the Agreement entered into force on 4 April 1995, upon expiration of the original Agreement.
<P>
<LI>The following States have notified the Agency of their acceptance of the extension of the Agreement.
