<HEAD>
<TITLE>
INFCIRC/449/Add. 1
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=left>
<IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/iaeasmal.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="IAEA LOGO">
