<FONT SIZE=+2><B>Information Circular</B></FONT>
<BR>
<SMALL><I>(Unofficial electronic edition)</I></SMALL>
</TD>
<TD ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=BOTTOM><SMALL><B><I>INFCIRC/449/Add.1
<BR>
4 August 1994
<P>
GENERAL Distr.
<BR>
Original: ARABIC, CHINESE, <BR>
ENGLISH, FRENCH, RUSSIAN, SPANISH
</I></B></SMALL>
</TD>
