<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER> <IMG SRC="../graphic/guest.gif" BORDER=0></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT  SIZE=6><B>Feedback Form</FONT></CENTER></B>
<P>
<B>After you browse and review the Home Page, we would appreciate
feedback in the following ways:</B>
<OL>
<LI>If you don't want to use our form please send your comments
on and send a message specifically relating to that page to: <A HREF="mailto:stanik@nepo1.iaea.or.at">Z. Stanik</A>
<LI>In addition to any feedback that this page-specific (as in
#1), please fill out this form providing your general impression
in the following areas:<BR>

</OL>

<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="/cgi-bin/inis.feedback.pl">

<P>
<INPUT NAME="TO" VALUE="stanik@nepo1.iaea.or.at" TYPE="HIDDEN">
<INPUT NAME="SUBJECT" VALUE="Bestellung" TYPE="HIDDEN"> <TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=65%><TR><TD><B>GRAPHICS</B>
- Do you feel that the graphics reflect well on the image of INIS?
Are the types and locations of buttons, section bars, etc. satisfactory?
Any suggestions for changes or improvements? (please be specific).
<P>

<TEXTAREA NAME="graphics" ROWS=4 COLS=45>

</TEXTAREA>

<P>
<B>NAVIGATION</B> - What is your opinion of the navigation through
the Home Page?
<P>

<TEXTAREA NAME="navigation" ROWS=4 COLS=45>

</TEXTAREA>

<P>
<B>SECTIONS</B> - What is your opinion of the main and sub-sections
of the Home Page? Is there anything else which should be included?
Anything that you'd prefer deleted?
<P>

<TEXTAREA NAME="sections" ROWS=4 COLS=45>

</TEXTAREA>

<P>
<B>CONTENT</B> - What is your opinion of the content currently
contained in the prototype?
<P>

<TEXTAREA NAME="content" ROWS=4 COLS=45>

</TEXTAREA>

<P>
<B>FEATURES</B> - The function buttons reflect functions that
provide fast access to certain areas. For example, the red Database
Access button is designed to allow INIS Database users with passwords
to directly access the Database upon entering the INIS Home Page.
- What do you think about these functions?
<P>

<TEXTAREA NAME="features" ROWS=4 COLS=45>

</TEXTAREA>

<P>
<B>TECHNICAL INFORMATION</B> - We need the following questions
answered, which describe your technical capability for using the
INIS Home Page
<P>
1) What type of Computer do you use?
<P>
