<OPTION>Memory Size
<OPTION>4 MB
<OPTION>8 MB
<OPTION>12 MB
<OPTION>16 MB
<OPTION>more than 16 MB
<OPTION>Other
<OPTION>Don't know</SELECT> 
<P>
3) How many colors does your monitor support?
