<P>
<FONT SIZE=6><B>INIS HOME PAGE</FONT> <BR>
<BR>
</CENTER><CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=5 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=6>
<IMG SRC="graphic/blueball.gif" BORDER="0"><B> </TD><TD VALIGN=top><FONT  SIZE=4><A HREF="glance/glance.htm">INIS AT A GLANCE</A></FONT>
</B></B>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
What is INIS? Is my country a member of INIS? These questions
and others are answered including background information on the
organization's history, mission, policy, etc. </TD>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

