<HEAD>

<TITLE>INIS at a Glance - Secretariat</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Stanik Zsolt">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="glance.htm"><IMG SRC="../graphic/glance.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
 <FONT SIZE=6>INIS Secretariat</FONT>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
The Secretariat function is vested in the Agency with Secretariat
functions being carried out by the <A HREF="../mail.htm">INIS Section, IAEA Division of Scientific and Technical Information</A>.
The Secretariat function is, therefore, carried out within IAEA
policies, procedures, channels of authority, and financial limitations.
The Secretariat has a Staff of approximately forty individuals
specializing in various aspects of the INIS activity. Click here
for <A HREF="../products/fulltext/schemati.htm">schematic</A>
which illustrates roles of INIS Secretariat and INIS Members.
For more information, contact:
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<UL>
<LI>Claudio Todeschini <BR>
Head, INIS Section <BR>
International Atomic Energy Agency <BR>
Wagramerstrasse 5 <BR>
P.O. Box 100 <BR>
A-1400 Vienna, Austria <BR>
Telephone: +43 1 2060 22875 <BR>
Telefax: +43 1 2060 29882 <BR>
Internet: <A HREF="mailto:mayer@nepo1.iaea.or.at">mayer@nepo1.iaea.or.at</A>
</UL>

<P>
<BR>
<BR>

