Prices include postage (airmail shipped for overseas)</I> 
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Information on prices is available from any INIS <A HREF="../../liaison/liaison.htm">Liaison Officer</A>
or from the INIS Clearinghouse . <BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

