<HEAD>

<TITLE>MARKETING AND PROMOTION</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Laura Roberson">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="../products.htm"><IMG SRC="../../graphic/prodserv.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=6>MARKETING AND PROMOTION</FONT> </CENTER>
<BR>
<HR>

<P>
<FONT SIZE=3>According to the &quot;Definition of Membership Arrangement
for INIS,&quot; each INIS Member is responsible for promoting
and marketing INIS products and services within its applicable
boundaries (or organizational confines if an international body).
The INIS Secretariat assists by providing general promotional
materials about INIS and its Database. These materials include,
for example, a brochure, <I> <A HREF="../../pdf/present.pdf">Presenting INIS</A>
, the <A HREF="../../pdf/perirep.pdf">INIS Periodic Report</A> </I>
, presentation visuals, an INIS display including a CD-ROM of
the INIS subject scope, etc. Members use different tools and opportunities
to provide information on the Database and its capabilities to
potential users and assist the actual users in improving their
skills at searching and retrieving information from the Database.
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=14>
<IMG SRC="../../graphic/blueball.gif" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14">
