<HEAD>

<TITLE>NEA Data Bank</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Laura Roberson">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="../products.htm"><IMG SRC="../../graphic/prodserv.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>
<BR>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE=6>NEA Data Bank</FONT> <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=3>The Nuclear Energy Agency (NEA) is a special agency
of OECD. It is based in Paris and promotes cooperation between
its members for development of peaceful nuclear energy.
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
The NEA Data Bank deals with nuclear science aspects and data
needs covering the whole fuel cycle and some non-energy applications.
It supplies nuclear data and computer program service to IAEA
Member States. Click <A HREF="http://www.nea.fr/html/dbdesc.html">here</A>
for more information on the OECD NEA Data Bank. </FONT><BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG src="../../graphic/toolbar.gif" usemap="#toolbar" BORDER=0 VSPACE=5>
