<P>
<A NAME="note_1">[1]</A>  See document GC(40)/ .
<P>
<A NAME="note_2">[2]</A>  The Appropriation Sections represent
the Agency's Major
Programmes.
<P>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<P>
<A NAME="note_3">[1]</A>  See document GC(40)/  , para  of the
Introduction.
<P>
