<HEAD>
<TITLE>GC(40)/11/Add. 1 - Article VI of the Statute - (b) Composition of Regional Groups</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=left>
