http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/GC/gc40/resolutions/1995/gc3910.html 193.81.60.210 19970114233045 text/html 24301
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 23:30:48 GMT
