<CENTER>
<H2>Facilities under Agency safeguards or containing safeguarded material on 31 December 1994</H2> 
</CENTER>
<P>
<HR SIZE=3>
<P>
<CENTER>
<I>Notes: Information is compiled from the IAEA Annual Report for 1994. Click here for other <A HREF=advisor.htmll>advisory notes.</I></A>
<P>
<HR SIZE=3>
<P>
