<HEAD>
<TITLE>
SAFEGUARDS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H3> Agreements providing for safeguards, other than those in connection with NPT or the Treaty of Tlatelolco, approved by the Board as of 31 December 1994 (a) </H3>
<H4><I>While the Agency is a party to each of the following agreements, only the State(s) party to them is (are) listed. (b)</I></H4>
<P>
<I>(Editor's note: Information compiled from the IAEA Annual Report for 1994. This presentation differs from the one in that report.)</I>
<P>
