<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Centres participating in AGRIS</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="NESI">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="NESI">
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#CDFF9B">
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=+1>
<STRONG>CENTRES PARTICIPATING IN AGRIS<BR>
CENTRES PARTICIPANT A AGRIS<BR>
CENTROS PARTICIPANTES EN AGRIS</STRONG>
</FONT>
<P>
<H4>November 1996</H4></CENTER>
<P>
<HR>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH="90%">
<TR>
