Head FAO/IAEA Agriculture and Biotechnology Laboratory</i><P>
17:30 - <b>Keynote presentation from NEA(OECD)</b> <BR><I>H.
M&eacute;tivier, Institut de Protection et de S&ucirc;ret&eacute;
Nucl&eacute;aire, OECD/NEA<BR>P. Waight, Medical Adviser, Bureau
of Radiation and Medical Devices, OECD/NEA</i>
<P>
17:50 - <b>Keynote presentation on results of projects of Germany
with Belarus, the Russian Federation and Ukraine</b><BR><I>R.
Hille, Forschungszentrum J&uuml;lich</i>
