<P> 
(2) The four 1949 Geneva Conventions to which the Protocols are additional relate, respectively, to: the  amelioration of the wounded and sick in armed forces in the field; the amelioration of the conditions of  wounded, sick and shipwrecked members of armed forces at sea; the treatment of prisoners of war; and the  protection of civilian persons in times of war. 
<P> 
